    "created_at": "2013-12-15T14:07:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-12-15T14:07:17Z",
    "body": "As I tried, it seems that on Windows a open dialog can be either a file chooser or a folder chooser, but not both. In atom-shell if both `openFile` and `openDirectory` options are set (which is used by Atom) a folder chooser would be showed. I think we should have both `Open File..` and `Open Directory...` menus on Windows? Or is there way to allow selecting files and directories in the same dialog?\n"
  },
