    "updated_at": "2013-12-15T20:50:19Z",
    "body": "Hm, I think in this case we need to rethink having the `openDirectory` option set on the Open file menu item - it really should _just_ be `openFile` in my opinion. The tree that Atom displays in the left should be the top-level Git repo of the file you just opened\n"
